Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莉亚露好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为火雾战士可是很笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是把在这里看见的一大朵花当成我们的弱点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是叫「Pinion」的磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}Pinion：通过泰莉亚露的自在法由人类变化而成的东西  原意为小齿轮  这里应该是有构成「摇篮花园」的部件的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是给弄坏一朵的话  还会再开的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  泰莉亚露  快把贽殿遮那给…已经可以了吧  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说的是啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那差不多该交出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  这种情况下还到处晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想大概是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是磷子的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要换地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听的到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个  果然是那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是以前说的另一个火雾战士的跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密斯提斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道是想报恩还是迷上了那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不动脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动脑子么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了啊  其他的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才有没有叫我们「小弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是终于承认我们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  比起这个快点行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  还不好意思呐  我纯情的…呜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对待方式大不一样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和亚拉斯托尔比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…刚才形成的像花一样的东西那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有像管道般不断传输着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在式仍旧混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火炬没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没问你为什么会在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为夏娜跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有收集存在之力的机关也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是在花开之前就察觉到那里有机关了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…有点感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要想破坏那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说基本没可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这混乱的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还能找到磷子的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会发生有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能帮到小鬼忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  我的贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  奖励是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  如果派上什么用场的话  给我奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜  我呢  是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴对嘴的Kiss是像发誓一般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙的…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试下刀如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想试想试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这刀身完全没有波动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥喜欢用新玩具在火雾战士身上试验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后从皮开始到肉  骨  内脏逐一地…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了这话不仅不恶语相向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连哭喊都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的这个是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带给哥哥欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此来满足我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们彼此编织着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想着讨伐的「王」的道具可没资格说三道四的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…只是相互依附着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对小孩子来说这话题是不是过于高尚了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和讨伐的道具来谈论爱真是毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来达成哥哥的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来保护哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个家伙与我和悠二…是不同的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背理  回归顺配列
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  就算再不唱歌  也不用念这么没情趣的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就是5个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个加油站前的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早敌人会有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处准确地破坏着Pinion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个火雾战士到底用了什么手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个火雾战士行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的记忆中可是\N「别管她  保护八音盒」这个命令来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话摇篮花园就会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是觉得不用管也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看中的东西不是已经到手了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  能看穿Pinion伪装的对手一定不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正从火雾战士手里保护你们也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间烧掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炎之剑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给自己的剑燃烧殆尽的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二会来的  悠二一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  讨伐的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人孤单的带着烧焦的身体去另一个世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非共存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是相互强烈地感受对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是火雾战士\N决心发誓履行维护世界的平衡这个使命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是指…这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然由你先找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真感激不尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀戮的美姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说无聊的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点露出本性如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为野兽来享受快乐正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临时拼凑也该适可而止吧  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说  好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天将会是最后一次见到也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在这附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个…上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊  悼词朗诵者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲哀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连悔恨的感情…也已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束它吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少下一个好点的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅伤口都再生  竟然而且还阻止了那火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还回来  我的贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  治疗哥哥的伤口和防御你的攻击使得力量不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做到这步…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我达成哥哥的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也感受一下这份无法抑制的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有个少年在那桥上移动着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密斯提斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给打的真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…但你也会耍些小把戏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在这里崩塌之前的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出替身人偶  消除气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让别人觉得你已经死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能唱歌的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经是尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先要看看外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你中招昏过去这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没动静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔克西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你期望的结果么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怠惰的愚者——玛裘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都萎靡不振
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算自己是空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找着和别人无关的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变成这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么理由向谁去抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  因为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我战斗了几百年了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶着银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算让我稍微休息下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这如果能被允许的话那可真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这个世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要…想这样振作起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从趴在地上开始  重新来过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔克…这到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  我可没吹牛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他们说你给埋在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没听到回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔唷  荣太  接近的话可危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大姐现在给痛打了一顿火气正旺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是认真又认真的状态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是  伤怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回玻璃坛去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  红世之徒什么的请尽管打飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是像傻瓜一样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那停手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有要保护的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道里面放了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼…悼词朗诵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战机也已成熟  真是个进攻的好时机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便士便士  便士攒起来的话就是有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛…不用即兴诗也不是还能打打么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是控制他们自在法的宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是操作摇篮花园的八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何复杂的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要装进去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多少次都可以自动使出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的贽殿遮那还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做蔷薇的花环吧  哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口袋里有好多花啊  嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…这样下去委托也不能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱染兄妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是炎发灼眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱染兄妹那样一来也撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千变」希德内逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事都请随心所欲地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边像是也搞定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那变态兄妹的自在式给我稍微做了点手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为像傻瓜一样收集存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把城市复原也应该足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  封绝马上就要解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  不快点回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦  那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看穿了Pinion  又找来悼词朗诵者帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你奖励…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之悠二不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对坂井同学说过「喜欢你」的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么事可以让狡猾的小缘来妨碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二是我的…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二和我在一起绝对比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由坂井同学来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明对悠二的事一无所知的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始就会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能就是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输…绝对不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个和她的诞生关系密切的女性——威尔艾米娜·卡梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.15,0:24:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐渐明朗的夏娜的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  伟大之人
